The father of Dave Brockie , the late frontman of the eccentric heavy metal band GWAR , has sued the group claiming they have stolen his son 's ashes , guitars and artwork .
Brockie was known onstage as the armor-clad demon Oderus Urungus , was found slumped in a chair at his Richmond , Virginia , home .
A medical examiner later determined the 50-year-old musician died of accidental drug overdose .
The lawsuit alleges the surviving members of GWAR swiped guitars , artwork , a gold record , tour souvenirs and his ashes .